      <title>澳大利亚总理将于周二提出重塑减税法案</title>
      <link>https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/australia-pm-introduce-bill-reshape-tax-cuts-tuesday-2024-02-03/</link>
      <description><![CDATA[澳大利亚总理安东尼·艾博内塞周日表示，澳大利亚政府将在本周对减税计划进行立法修改，以减少富人的福利，同时为低收入者提供更多休息，因为澳大利亚人要承受更高的生活成本。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/australia-pm-introduce-bill-reshape-tax-cuts-tuesday-2024-02-03/</guid>
      <pubDate>Sat, 03 Feb 2024 23:38:57 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>中国碧桂园称30多个项目得到地方政府支持</title>
      <link>https://www.reuters.com/world/china/chinas-country-garden-says-over-30-projects-have-local-government-support-2024-02-03/</link>
      <description><![CDATA[资金短缺的开发商碧桂园周六表示，其30多个项目已被中国地方政府列为适合融资支持的项目，当局旨在向受危机打击的行业注入流动性。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.reuters.com/world/china/chinas-country-garden-says-over-30-projects-have-local-government-support-2024-02-03/</guid>
      <pubDate>Sat, 03 Feb 2024 14:39:38 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>印度将于五月前用文职人员取代驻马尔代夫的军队</title>
      <link>https://www.reuters.com/world/india-replace-troops-maldives-with-civilians-by-may-2024-02-03/</link>
      <description><![CDATA[马尔代夫外交部周六表示，印度将在五月前从马尔代夫撤军，两国正在寻求就撤军达成协议，这导致两国关系紧张。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.reuters.com/world/india-replace-troops-maldives-with-civilians-by-may-2024-02-03/</guid>
      <pubDate>Sat, 03 Feb 2024 11:40:01 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>韩国因批评尹总统言论而召见俄罗斯特使</title>
      <link>https://www.reuters.com/world/south-korea-summons-russian-envoy-over-criticism-president-yoons-remarks-foreign-2024-02-03/</link>
      <description><![CDATA[韩国外交部周六召见俄罗斯驻首尔特使，就莫斯科批评韩国总统尹锡烈最近关于朝鲜寻求核武库的言论提出投诉。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.reuters.com/world/south-korea-summons-russian-envoy-over-criticism-president-yoons-remarks-foreign-2024-02-03/</guid>
      <pubDate>Sat, 03 Feb 2024 11:20:24 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>泰国与斯里兰卡签署自由贸易协定</title>
      <link>https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/thailand-sri-lanka-sign-free-trade-agreement-2024-02-03/</link>
      <description><![CDATA[泰国和斯里兰卡周六签署了自由贸易协定，斯里兰卡希望此举将帮助其摆脱数十年来最严重的金融危机。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/thailand-sri-lanka-sign-free-trade-agreement-2024-02-03/</guid>
      <pubDate>Sat, 03 Feb 2024 10:57:22 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>伊姆兰·汗和他的妻子因非法婚姻被判处七年监禁</title>
      <link>https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/pakistan-ex-pm-imran-khan-wife-get-7-years-unlawful-marriage-ary-news-2024-02-03/</link>
      <description><![CDATA[近日，汗因泄露国家机密罪被判处10年徒刑，并因非法出售国家礼品罪与他的妻子一起被判处14年徒刑。他的代表表示，他将提出上诉。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/pakistan-ex-pm-imran-khan-wife-get-7-years-unlawful-marriage-ary-news-2024-02-03/</guid>
      <pubDate>Sat, 03 Feb 2024 10:55:09 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>印尼央行：应有降息空间，等待卢比走强</title>
      <link>https://www.reuters.com/markets/asia/indonesia-cbank-should-be-room-cut-rates-awaiting-stronger-rupiah-2024-02-03/</link>
      <description><![CDATA[印尼央行行长佩里·沃吉约(Perry Warjiyo)周六表示，印尼央行今年有降息空间以提振经济增长，但正在等待卢比兑美元走强。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.reuters.com/markets/asia/indonesia-cbank-should-be-room-cut-rates-awaiting-stronger-rupiah-2024-02-03/</guid>
      <pubDate>Sat, 03 Feb 2024 09:45:41 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>朝鲜睫毛如何以“中国制造”的身份进入西方</title>
      <link>https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/how-north-korean-eyelashes-make-their-way-west-made-china-2024-02-03/</link>
      <description><![CDATA[睫毛为朝鲜提供了规避制裁的途径，提供了重要的外汇。]]></description>
